OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and bright day with
OL,6,Fplenty of sunshine, the best in the
OL,7,Fmorning with some high cloud arriving
OL,8,Fin the afternoon. Lighter winds, a
OL,9,Fgentle southerly later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will be dry through the
OL,12,Fevening and overnight with largely
OL,13,Fclear skies and a touch of grass frost
OL,14,Fdeveloping.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FIt will be sunny, breezy and
OL,17,Fwarm, though feeling cool along North
OL,18,FSea coasts. Turning cloudier later
OL,19,Fwith some rain in the west in the
OL,20,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
