OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FCloudy
OL,6,FWednesday morning but bright spells
OL,7,Fdeveloping, dry, bright and warm by
OL,8,Fday. Cooler with sunshine and showers
OL,9,Fon Thursday. Bright start on Friday,
OL,10,Fthen turning windier with some rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
